      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNDER ANESTHETIC (8) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (30.77) last time in a NG at Taree Super Track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and a minor placing from five starts. Can make amends. IT'S A TEASE (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Hi Lo Rain (29.99) in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Has a solid record from this box including five wins and a minor placing. Expecting another good run. KAREN STRATUS (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.54) from Box 2 at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Will give a great sight again.",
